title: VA-Let The Music Do The Talking 3CDs Classic Rock
description:
VA - Let The Music Do The Talking [2008] 3 CD Set @ 128kbps


A superb, fully tagged, MP3 player ready introduction to many of the great rock sounds from the late Seventies and early Eighties. Check it out ... Enjoy ... And definitely buy the music of the artists you find particularly interesting.

Seed for as long as possible for all to hear!
